notes: Coverage analysis based on explicit test assertions. Tests validate high-level response structure (OBL-SCHEMA-002, OBL-SCHEMA-003, OBL-SCHEMA-004) and itinerary field presence/types (OBL-ITIN-002, OBL-ITIN-003, OBL-ITIN-004, OBL-ITIN-005), but most implementation-level contracts (Pydantic schema validation, LLM output parsing, configuration constraints, routing logic, tool signatures, state management internals, normalization fallback logic, and tracing) are not explicitly validated. Tests check output properties but not the underlying enforcement mechanisms, parsing behavior, configuration values, routing decisions, tool function signatures, state structure, normalization error handling, or tracing attributes. Only temperature check in determinism test covers OBL-CONFIG-001 partially by reading config.temperature but not asserting it equals 0.0.
